Awards and nominations
In 1993, he received the Rafael &lt;U+00C1&gt;lvarez Ovalle Order from the then President of Guatemala, Ramiro de Le&lt;U+00F3&gt;n Carpio, for his international accomplishments.202 At USAC a library hall bears his name.203 His birthplace, Jocotenango, named a street after him.204
